BAPE x Old Skool 36 DX 'Green Camo'
results.story: The BAPE x Vans Old Skool 36 DX ‘Green Camo’ showcases the Japanese streetwear brand’s signature allover print. The low-top carries an upper that combines olive green suede with canvas construction in BAPE’s ABC Camo, rendered in a traditional blend of brown, green, grey, and khaki hues. A white leather side stripe cuts through the side panel, while the custom sockliner features a traditional Vans logo with an Ape Head icon. The sneaker sits atop a white vulcanized rubber midsole, accented with a black foxing stripe and supported by a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole.

results.name: BAPE x Sk8-Hi 36 DX 'Multi Camo'
results.story: The BAPE x Vans Sk8-Hi 36 DX ‘Multi Camo’ combines asymmetrical color blocking with a traditional canvas and suede build. A custom version of BAPE’s ABC Camo print is a common through-line on each canvas side panel, rendered in mismatched finishes and accented with a white leather side stripe. Mismatched hues are similarly applied to the sneaker’s suede components, including each eyestay, toe box, and heel overlay. Underpinning the high-top is a traditional waffle-traction outsole in grippy gum rubber.

Vans Vault OG CLassic Slip-On LX Geoff McFetridge
results.story: The Geoff McFetridge x Vans Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX ‘Transcentcoastal’ is taken from a capsule collection released in partnership with the LA-based artist and illustrator. The low-top carries a color-blocked textile upper featuring a pink quarter panel, indigo heel overlay, and a green vamp with contrasting green tan trim. Inside the shoe, a blue sailboat graphic enlivens the insole and interior lining. A waffle-tread gum rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Vans Authentic 44 DX Bape 1st Camo
results.story: Drawn from a capsule collection with the influential streetwear label, the BAPE x Vans Authentic 44 DX ‘First Camo’ combines the partner brands’ signature design hallmarks. BAPE’s 1st Camo print is executed in woodland hues on Vans’ traditional canvas upper, mounted on a crisp white rubber midsole with a contrasting black foxing stripe. Inside the shoe, a crimson sockliner features dual BAPE and Vans branding. A matching red waffle-traction outsole delivers grippy traction.

results.name: Vans Sk8-Hi 38 DX Bape Line ABC Camo
results.story: Dropping as part of a capsule collection with the pioneering streetwear brand, the BAPE x Vans Sk8-Hi 38 DX ‘Lined Camo’ features a simple two-tone palette with unexpected pops of color. BAPE’s signature ABC camo print is outlined in white on the black canvas upper, fortified with tonal suede construction on the forefoot and heel overlay. A white leather jazz stripe cuts across the side panel, while Vans’ crimson Off the Wall logo adorns the camo-print tongue tag. Underfoot, a matching red hue floods the waffle-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Vans Vault Sk8-Hi Cap LX Mastermind World Presented by END.
Vans Vault Old Skool Mastermind World presented by END.
results.story: The END. x Mastermind Japan x Vand Old Skool ‘Black’ updates the vintage silhouette with a unique cut-and-paste aesthetic, highlighted by an unfinished, exposed foam collar and doubled-up tongues. Molded white side stripes adorn an upper built with a combination of black canvas, leather and suede. ‘Mastermind Japan’ is embroidered on the toe box, while the brand’s skull and crossbones graphic appears on the medial eyestay and lateral heel. The sneaker rides on a black rubber midsole, featuring a contrasting white toe bumper and ‘Mastermind’ etched in block lettering on the lateral sidewall. Underfoot, a translucent rubber outsole reveals Vans’ black and white checkerboard print.

results.name: END. x Mastermind Japan x Old Skool 'White'
results.story: The END. x Mastermind Japan x Vans Old Skool ‘White’ brings Masaaki Homma’s meticulous vision and rebellious attitude to the vintage skate shoe. A one-note ivory finish is executed on the upper, built with a traditional bend of canvas, leather and suede. The sneaker’s side stripes are molded and raised, while the low-cut collar is unfinished, leaving the interior foam padding exposed. Additional details include doubled-up tongues and Vans’ checkerboard print on the medial side panel. Anchoring the low-top is an off-white rubber midsole with ‘Mastermind’ stamped in block lettering on the lateral sidewall. Underfoot, a black and white checkerboard pattern is revealed beneath the translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Supreme x Half Cab 'Barbed Wire - White'
results.story: Made exclusively for the New York skate brand, the Supreme x Vans Half Cab ‘Barbed Wire’ adds a graphic element to a two-tone colorway of the classic skate shoe. The upper is constructed from off-white suede with contrasting black accents on the laces, padded tongue, and woven Half Cab labels. The sneaker is mounted on a black vulcanized rubber midsole, accented with a white barbed wire graphic and a crimson Supreme-branded license plate at the heel.

results.name: Supreme x Old Skool 'Barbed Wire - Royal'
results.story: The Supreme x Vans Old Skool ‘Barbed Wire’ delivers the New York skate brand’s take on the vintage silhouette that debuted in 1977 as the Vans #36. The low-top features a royal blue canvas upper with charcoal suede overlays and a color-matched leather side stripe. A dual-branded tag adorns the interior tongue, while a Supreme wordmark is debossed on the heel overlay. The sneaker sits atop a white vulcanized rubber midsole, accented with a wraparound barbed wire graphic and a red license plate at the heel.

results.name: Vans Vault Sk8-Hi Cap LX MASTERMIND World Marshmallow
results.story: The END. x Mastermind Japan x Vans Sk8-Hi ‘White’ presents a reconstructed take on the heritage skate shoe. A monochrome off-white is applied to the mixed material build, highlighted by an asymmetrical blend of leather, canvas and suede. The lateral side features zip closure, an elongated eyestay, and a leather side stripe with exposed zigzag stitching. A perforated side stripe accompanies Mastermind’s signature skull and crossbones graphic on the medial side. The high-top is mounted on a deconstructed midsole, featuring exaggerated proportions and misaligned details. Underfoot, Vans’ signature checkerboard print enlivens the translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Supreme x Old Skool 'Barbed Wire - Green'
results.story: The Supreme x Vans Old Skool ‘Barbed Wire’ is drawn from a footwear collection with the iconic New York skate brand. The upper combines light green canvas with burgundy suede overlays and a white leather side stripe. A traditional Vans tag hangs off the lateral eyestay, while a Supreme wordmark is debossed on the heel overlay. The sneaker rides on a white vulcanized rubber midsole, featuring a wraparound barbed wire graphic, a black foxing stripe, and a red Supreme-branded license plate.

results.name: Vans Old Skool Mastermind World presented by END. White
Supreme x Half Cab 'Barbed Wire - Light Blue'
results.story: Launching as part of the New York skate brand’s Fall/Winter 2021 collection, the Supreme x Vans Half Cab ‘Barbed Wire’ features a light blue suede upper with white contrast stitching and a woven Half Cab tag on the lateral ankle. A padded tongue and Vans’ PopCush insole deliver a comfortable fit. The sneaker is mounted on a black vulcanized rubber midsole, accented with a wraparound barbed wire graphic and a Supreme-branded red license plate at the heel. Underfoot, a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole delivers optimal grip.

results.name: Supreme x Half Cab 'Barbed Wire - Burgundy'
results.story: Dropping as part of a footwear collaboration with the pioneering New York skate brand, the Supreme x Vans Half Cab ‘Barbed Wire’ features a burgundy suede upper with contrasting black accents and white stitching throughout. Half Cab branding appears on the tongue tag and a woven label stitched atop the lateral ankle. Inside the shoe, Vans’ PopCush sockliner provides lightweight cushioning. A barbed wire graphic enlivens the black rubber midsole, supported by a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole. Supreme branding appears on the red license plate at the heel.

results.name: END. x Mastermind Japan x Sk8-Hi 'Black'
results.story: The END. x Mastermind Japan x Vans Sk8-Hi ‘Black’ is taken from a capsule collection that reimagines the classic silhouette with a rebellious punk-rock sensibility. Mastermind’s signature skull and crossbones graphic is plastered across a black canvas backdrop on the medial side, while the opposite side features black suede construction with zippered closure, an elongated black leather eyestay, and a white leather side stripe. Atop the tongue, a woven Vans tag is accessorized with metal hardware. Anchoring the sneaker is a deconstructed rubber midsole with misaligned paneling. Underfoot, a translucent rubber outsole reveals Vans’ signature checkerboard print.

results.name: Supreme x Half Cab 'Barbed Wire - Black'
results.story: The Supreme x Vans Half Cab ‘Barbed Wire’ is taken from a footwear collection that reunites the familiar partner brands from New York and Southern California. This pair makes use of a black suede upper with white contrast stitching and traditional Half Cab branding. A padded tongue combines with Vans’ PopCush sockliner to deliver a comfortable fit. A white barbed wire graphic garlands the black vulcanized rubber midsole, supported underfoot by a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole. A red Supreme-branded license plate provides a solitary pop of color.

results.name: Supreme x Old Skool 'Barbed Wire - Pink'
results.story: The Supreme x Vans Old Skool ‘Barbed Wire’ is taken from a footwear collection with the iconic New York skate brand founded in 1994. The low-top features a pink canvas upper with a yellow leather side stripe and black suede overlays at the forefoot and heel. The latter is marked with a Supreme wordmark in white debossed lettering. Black leather lines the interior, while a PopCush insole provides lightweight cushioning. A black barbed wire graphic wraps around the white rubber midsole, accented with a red Supreme-branded license plate at the heel.

Nigel Cabourn x OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Carpet Green Mix'
results.story: The Nigel Cabourn x Vans OG Classic Slip-On LX ‘Carpet Green Mix’ features a unique design inspired by a vintage chair that the British designer discovered during one of his trips to California. A multicolor jacquard weave enlivens the upper, bound in olive green trim and lined in camouflage-print textile. ‘Nigel Cabourn’ is embossed on a pair of eyelets embedded in each quarter panel, while dual branding decorates the custom sockliner. The sneaker rides on an off-white rubber midsole, accented with red pinstripe detailing and supported by a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Nigel Cabourn x OG Classic Slip-On LX 'USMC Army Mix'
results.story: Taken from a capsule collection with the British menswear designer, the Nigel Cabourn x Vans OG Classic Slip-On LX ‘USMC Army Mix’ applies varying shades of green to an upper built with cotton and herringbone — the same materials used to manufacture US Army uniforms in the late 1930s. Details include rip-and-repair stitching and branded eyelets inspired by drainage ports used in US military boots. The sneaker is mounted on an olive drab vulcanized rubber midsole with tonal license plate branding and a tan foxing stripe.

results.name: Vans Vault OG Authentic LX Nigel Cabourn Army Camo
results.story: Dropping as part of an apparel and footwear collection with the British menswear designer, the Nigel Cabourn x Vans OG Authentic LX ‘Army Green Camo’ draws inspiration from a WW2 USMC HBT shirt. A green and red camo pattern suffuses the aged cotton canvas upper, featuring branded eyelets and rip-and-repair stitching. Cabourn’s signature broad arrow is embroidered on the tongue, while his name is emblazoned on the sockliner. The lace-up rides on a vulcanized rubber midsole, underpinned by Vans’ waffle-traction outsole in sticky gum rubber.

results.name: Vans Vault OG Authentic LX Nigel Cabourn Navy Mix
results.story: The Nigel Cabourn x Vans OG Authentic LX ‘Crazy Navy Mix’ delivers the British menswear designer’s color-blocked interpretation of the classic lace-up. Inspired by vintage US naval workwear, the sneaker features an aged canvas build with dark navy paneling on the forefoot, vibrant indigo on the lateral side panel, neutral grey on the medial side, and a bright red heel strip outlined in contrasting black stitching. An embroidered broad arrow decorates the tongue, while Nigel Cabourn branding is embossed on the sneaker’s eyelets. Underfoot, a waffle-tread gum rubber outsole offers grippy traction.

results.name: Vans OG Style 24 LX Nigel Cabourn Denim
results.story: Drawn from a capsule collection with the British menswear designer, the Nigel Cabourn x Vans OG Style 24 LX High ‘Denim’ showcases a dark navy finish on a mixed-material build. The sneaker’s tongue and lateral side are constructed from cotton canvas, while the medial side panel is rendered in herringbone twill. Details include branded eyelets, a white rubber toe cap and a red embroidered arrow atop the tongue. The high-top rests on a solid white rubber midsole, reinforced underfoot by a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Vans Vault OG Authentic LX Nigel Cabourn Natural Navy
results.story: Releasing as part of a capsule collection with the British designer, the Nigel Cabourn x Vans OG Authentic LX ‘USN’ takes inspiration from US Naval deck plimsolls from the Second World War. The low-top makes use of a tan cotton canvas upper with rip-and-repair stitching and branded eyelets. Cabourn’s embroidered broad arrow decorates the tongue, while ‘USN’ is stenciled on each toe box. The sneaker rests on a navy vulcanized rubber midsole with a contrasting red foxing stripe.

results.name: Nigel Cabourn x OG Style 24 LX 'Navy Ventile'
results.story: Releasing as part of an expansive collection with the British menswear designer, the Nigel Cabourn x Vans OG Style 24 LX ‘Navy Ventile’ showcases a monochrome palette on a low-top edition of a vintage skate shoe originally released in the ‘80s. The upper is crafted from water-resistant navy cotton Ventile with a tonal rubber toe cap and branded eyelets. Contrasting scarlet accents appear on an embroidered arrow atop the tongue and dual pinstripe detailing on the navy rubber midsole.

results.story: The Sneakersnstuff x Vans Vault OG Authentic LX ‘Venice’ features an archival ‘90s print throughout the off-white canvas upper. The design is updated with references to Sneakersnstuff’s seven retail doors, including illustrations that nod to the sunny Venice Beach location. A peach-colored Vans tag adds a discreet pop of color to the lateral forefoot, while graffiti-style ‘SNS’ branding decorates the rubber midsole in a repeating pattern. Vans’ signature waffle tread provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: JJJJound x Sk8-Mid Vault LX 'Green'
results.story: Designed in partnership with Justin Saunders’ blog turned brand, the JJJJound x Vans Sk8-Mid Vault LX ‘Green’ showcases a military-inspired palette on the sneaker that debuted in 1978 as the Style 37. The upper pairs khaki textile with olive suede paneling along the toe box, eyestay and heel. Details include a white leather jazz stripe, a woven Vans tongue tag, and a discreet JJJJound tag affixed to the heel overlay. The mid-top sits on a white vulcanized rubber midsole with a contrasting black foxing stripe and Off the Wall license plate.

results.name: JJJJound x Sk8-Mid Vault LX 'Brown'
results.story: Launching as part of a three-piece pack with Justin Saunders’ menswear label, the JJJJound x Vans Sk8-Mid Vault LX ‘Brown’ confers a simple-two tone palette to the shoe that debuted in 1978 as the Style 37. A white leather jazz stripe cuts through the canvas side panel, while contrast white stitching enlivens the suede toe box, eyestay and heel overlay. The latter is accented with a small JJJJound tag on the lateral side. The mid-top is mounted on a white vulcanized rubber midsole, which gives way to a matching white waffle-traction outsole.

results.name: JJJJound x Sk8-Mid Vault LX 'Black'
results.story: Developed in partnership with the Montreal-based brand, the JJJJound x Vans Sk8-Mid Vault LX ‘Black’ delivers a stealthy, minimalist interpretation of the vintage silhouette. Contrast white stitching distinguishes the classic lines of the blacked-out upper, built with a traditional blend of canvas and suede. Branding elements include a tonal leather jazz stripe and a small JJJJound tag affixed to the heel overlay. The sneaker rests on a white vulcanized rubber midsole, accented with a black foxing stripe and Vans’ Off the Wall license plate.

Vans Wayvee Dime Egret
results.story: The Dime x Vans Wayvee ‘Egret’ introduces a new silhouette designed in partnership with the Montreal-based skate brand. A neutral cream-colored finish is applied to an upper constructed from translucent textile with tonal suede overlays. Performance benefits include a reinforced DURACAP toe and Vans’ LuxLiner bootie construction, which integrates the tongue and interior lining for a snug, sock-like fit. Underfoot, Dime branding is visible beneath a translucent waffle-traction outsole.

results.name: Vans Authentic Bedwin And The Heartbreakers Multi Yellow Bandana
results.story: Launching as part of a four-piece ‘Bandana Pack’ designed in collaboration with the Tokyo-based fashion brand, the Bedwin & The Heartbreakers x Vans Authentic ‘Multi A’ features a paneled textile upper made with cut-and-sewn pieces derived from American-made bandanas. The low-top sits on a white vulcanized rubber midsole with a red foxing stripe and matching red license plate. Underfoot, Vans’ waffle-traction rubber outsole is rendered in a bright yellow finish.

results.name: Vans Authentic Bedwin And The Heartbreakers Multi Purple Bandana
results.story: Conceived in partnership with the Tokyo-based fashion brand, the Bedwin & The Heartbreakers x Vans Authentic ‘Multi B’ is taken from the four-piece ‘Bandana Pack.’ Like its companion colorways, this pair features a textile upper crafted from pieces of American-made bandanas that are cut and sewn to produce one-of-a-kind designs. The various paisley prints up top are offset by crisp white rubber midsole with a contrasting black foxing stripe. A yellow waffle-traction rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.
